OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780369437
OL,3,CConfidence in universities falling
OL,4,Camid concern over loans and jobs `
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FConfidence in the value of going to
OL,8,Funiversity has slumped amid declining
OL,9,Fjob prospects and anger over student
OL,10,Fdebt, a major survey of public opinion
OL,11,Fhas found.
OL,13,FThe latest British Social Attitudes
OL,14,F(BSA) survey found fewer people
OL,15,Fbelieve university is worth the time
OL,16,Fand money than 20 years ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780369437
OL,3,CConfidence in universities falling
OL,4,Camid concern over loans and jobs `
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FThe number of people saying it is not
OL,8,Fworth going to university hit a record
OL,9,Fhigh of 34% last year, more than twice
OL,10,Fthe 15% who said the same thing in
OL,11,F2005.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, the belief that graduates
OL,14,Fare better off in the long run has
OL,15,Fcollapsed from 50% in 2005 to 36%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780369437
OL,3,CConfidence in universities falling
OL,4,Camid concern over loans and jobs `
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FThe findings of the BSA come amid
OL,8,Fpressure to reform the student loan
OL,9,Fsystem, with recent graduates
OL,10,Fdescribing it as unfair due to high
OL,11,Finterest rates and the unlikelihood of
OL,12,Fpaying off the debt.
OL,14,FAt the same time, opportunities for
OL,15,Fgraduates have reduced, with 700,000
OL,16,Fnow out of work and receiving benefits
OL,17,F` an increase of 200,000 since 2019,
OL,18,Faccording to the Centre for Social
OL,19,FJustice think tank.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780369437
OL,3,CConfidence in universities falling
OL,4,Camid concern over loans and jobs `
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FSome politicians have also called for
OL,8,Fa reduction in student numbers and a
OL,9,Fgreater focus on vocational education,
OL,10,Fwith both the Conservatives and Reform
OL,11,FUK backing cuts in numbers.
OL,13,FBut the BSA most people continue to
OL,14,Fbelieve that opportunities for young
OL,15,Fpeople to go to university should
OL,16,Feither increase or remain the same,
OL,17,Fwith only 18% backing a reduction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780369437
OL,3,CConfidence in universities falling
OL,4,Camid concern over loans and jobs `
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FHowever, some 42% of people also said
OL,8,Fthere were too many recent graduates,
OL,9,Frising to 49% among those with
OL,10,Fdegrees, with only 10% of the public
OL,11,Fsaying there were not enough.
OL,13,FAlex Scholes, a BSA co-author, warned
OL,14,Fthat declining confidence in
OL,15,Funiversities risked further
OL,16,Fexacerbating financial problems in the
OL,17,Fhigher education sector.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780369437
OL,3,CConfidence in universities falling
OL,4,Camid concern over loans and jobs `
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FHe said: "Universities are not just
OL,8,Feducation institutions, they are
OL,9,Fengines of social mobility and
OL,10,Feconomic growth, and play a vital role
OL,11,Fin defining Britain's cultural role on
OL,12,Fthe world stage.
OL,14,F"They are also under immense financial
OL,15,Fpressure, and it appears recent
OL,16,Fdebates about the fairness of student
OL,17,Floan repayment systems and the role of
OL,18,FAI on the job market have filtered
OL,19,Fthrough to people's views about the
OL,20,Fvalue of a degree.
OL,26,@oD@JOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780369437
OL,3,CConfidence in universities falling
OL,4,Camid concern over loans and jobs `
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,F"If public confidence continues to
OL,8,Ffall, we risk seeing the financial
OL,9,Fsituation become even worse."
OL,11,FThe annual BSA survey was carried out
OL,12,Fby the National Centre for Social
OL,13,FResearch between August and October
OL,14,F2025, and polled 4,656 people across
OL,15,Fthe UK.
